Andries du Plessis Jr outplayed 73 other golfers during Polokwane Golf Club s club day on Saturday to claim victory with 44 points. In second place was Aart Juriaanse on 39 points followed by Zach Chuenyane, also with 39 points, third. Kobus Marnewick landed nearest to the pin on the eighth hole and Walter du Plessis on the 11th. Story and photos: RC Myburgh &gt;&gt;rc.observer@gmail.com Walter du Plessis takes a final shot onto the green. He was nearest to the pin on the 11th hole. Thys de Kock tees off.